abraflexi-yearend (0.2.3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Compile .mo translation catalogs during the build (pybabel compile -
    d translations) instead of relying on committed binaries; *.mo is
    gitignored so the package previously shipped only .po sources and
    localization silently fell back to raw msgid keys.

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Sat, 04 Jul 2026 11:31:38 +0200

abraflexi-yearend (0.2.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix systemd unit invoking gunicorn as wsgi:app; wsgi.py exposes
    'application', not 'app', causing the service to crash-loop on every
    start.

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Sat, 04 Jul 2026 09:40:19 +0200

abraflexi-yearend (0.2.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix debian/abraflexi-yearend.install shadowing debian/install, which
